# NocoDB Integrations Source Map

This rule provides navigation guidance for the NocoDB integrations monorepo.

## Core Package

- [core/src/integration.ts](mdc:core/src/integration.ts): Base `IntegrationWrapper` class that all integrations extend
- [core/src/index.ts](mdc:core/src/index.ts): Main exports for the core package

### Integration Types

- [core/src/ai/types.ts](mdc:core/src/ai/types.ts): AI integration abstract class and interfaces
- [core/src/auth/types.ts](mdc:core/src/auth/types.ts): Auth integration abstract class and interfaces
- [core/src/sync/types.ts](mdc:core/src/sync/types.ts): Sync integration abstract class and interfaces

## Integration Packages

Each integration package follows this structure:

- `src/index.ts`: Exports the integration entry point with the `IntegrationEntry` object
- `src/integration.ts`: Implementation of the integration class extending appropriate base class
- `src/form.ts`: Form definition for configuration UI
- `src/manifest.ts`: Integration metadata (title, icon, version, etc.)

### AI Integrations
- [packages/openai-ai](mdc:packages/openai-ai): OpenAI integration implementation
- [packages/nocodb-ai](mdc:packages/nocodb-ai): NocoDB AI implementation

### Auth Integrations
- [packages/github-auth](mdc:packages/github-auth): GitHub authentication integration
- [packages/gitlab-auth](mdc:packages/gitlab-auth): GitLab authentication integration
- [packages/clickhouse-auth](mdc:packages/clickhouse-auth): ClickHouse authentication integration

### Sync Integrations
- [packages/github-sync](mdc:packages/github-sync): GitHub sync integration
- [packages/gitlab-sync](mdc:packages/gitlab-sync): GitLab sync integration
